    TITLE  :  Configuring 386MAX to Work with BCX










  BCX may report that there is not enough extended memory available
  when running under 386MAX.  To fix this problem use the following
  line in your config.sys file:

                  device = path\386max.sys pro=path\386max.pro

  where 386MAX.PRO is a file which contains the following line:

                  EXT=2048


































